That said, i believe only a handful of names in this market are actually going to be successful LT (marvell, lumentum, coherent, etc). CPO is still early...you wont see meaningful", "id_str": "2073159284662100328", "in_reply_to_screen_name": "SignalDesk_AB", "in_reply_to_status_id_str": "2073158618518835565", "in_reply_to_user_id_str": "1982662379281514496", "is_quote_status": false, "lang": "en", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 0, "retweet_count": 0, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "1650268779786452992"}, "note_tweet": {"is_expandable": true, "note_tweet_results": {"result": {"entity_set": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNzMxNTkyODQ1OTUwODEyMTY=", "media": {"inline_media": []}, "richtext": {"richtext_tags": []}, "text": "Im not personally in photonics, i just share this info because it may be of use to someone. 

That said, i believe only a handful of names in this market are actually going to be successful LT (marvell, lumentum, coherent, etc). CPO is still early...you wont see meaningful revenue until 2027-2028. A lot of people are getting ahead and investing in overvalued photonics stocks, hence the sharp pullback its see the past few weeks. At some point the valuation will matter, and its mattering now."}}}, "rest_id": "2073159284662100328", "source": "<a href="https://mobile.twitter.com" rel="nofollow">Twitter Web App</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "320", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

